Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.40,0:00:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.40,0:00:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基连总帅战死了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.95,0:00:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,0:00:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿·巴瓦·库已全权
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.20,0:00:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,移交给基希莉亚阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.70,0:00:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阴谋啊！基希莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.35,0:00:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦的杂鱼们！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.90,0:00:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集结全舰以及全MS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.90,0:00:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs34\3c&H00ef877e}MS：Mobile Space Utility Instruments Tactical\N(战术性泛用宇宙机动机械)的缩写
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.65,0:00:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我舰队撤离此空域
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.40,0:00:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉，不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.10,0:00:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已下了撤退命令
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.85,0:00:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！卡多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.20,0:01:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的母舰多洛瓦被击沉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.15,0:01:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多洛瓦？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.75,0:01:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的总帅基连阁下也逝世了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.90,0:01:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要撤离阿·巴瓦·库
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.70,0:01:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须活下去继承总帅的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.25,0:01:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要我苟且偷生吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.95,0:01:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.41,0:01:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.25,0:01:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在要忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.90,0:01:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在手握活着才能得到的那份荣光为止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.00,0:01:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的性命就托付于我！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.85,0:01:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.45,0:01:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为一年战争中最大激战的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.62,0:01:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿·巴瓦·库一役后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.00,0:01:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球联邦政府与ZION共和国
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.00,0:01:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs34\3c&H00ef877e}ZION：太空殖民地SIDE3独立时取ZION作为国名，与联邦对立
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.55,0:01:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缔结了终战协定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.95,0:01:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那只意味着新一轮战斗的开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.40,0:01:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)\fs60}GUNDAM 抢夺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.90,0:02:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这烂ZAKU！动作这么迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.90,0:02:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs34\3c&H00ef877e}ZAKU：型号MS-05，最早开发投入实战的MS\N一年战争中ZION的主力MS，并衍生出大量的型号
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.35,0:02:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟强化后的GM根本没得比
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.35,0:02:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs34\3c&H00ef877e}GM：GUNDAM Massproduction的缩写，型号RGM-79\N根据RX-78简化再设计的量产机，联邦MS的骨干
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.55,0:02:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏、吉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.90,0:02:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,采取第三阵形
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.00,0:02:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口气干掉它！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.65,0:02:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.58,0:02:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.20,0:02:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉斯少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有好好学过驾驶吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得手了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！这是什么推进力！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.40,0:03:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那背包对GM来说太笨重了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装在ZAKU上一定很配
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.60,0:03:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉斯，你逼紧GM
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.40,0:03:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面是殖民地残骸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.85,0:03:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绕到前面去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.30,0:03:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跟得上就很不容易了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.50,0:04:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太、太快了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.50,0:04:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有搞错，怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.30,0:04:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴宁格大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉斯机陷入残骸无法动弹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.75,0:04:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要进行回收
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂且原地待机吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待会再来回收
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了、了解…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.90,0:04:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴宁格大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.95,0:04:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GM的追加喷射器的数据不足
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.40,0:04:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距极限推力还有相当的余力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.10,0:04:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿连中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.10,0:04:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是巴宁格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将追加喷射器的推力全开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.90,0:04:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续进行模拟战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.30,0:04:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.40,0:05:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕沙洛夫大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.85,0:05:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有异常吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我擅自进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.75,0:05:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席那普斯舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系，巴普尔顿小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.05,0:05:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过从贾布罗到这几乎都是海洋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定很闷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.35,0:05:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.30,0:05:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便同样是海
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.50,0:05:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不同地点的海流和颜色也会不断变换
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.75,0:05:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了，这是你第一次来地球吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.30,0:05:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快到澳大利亚大陆了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:05:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.05,0:06:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚经过了昔日的悉尼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今所见的海洋曾是一片陆地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是ZION的“不列颠作战”造成的伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是殖民地的坠落痕迹？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大直径达五百公里的弹坑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.95,0:06:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史上最大的人工坑穴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相当于六万MegaTon级的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.10,0:06:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为战争的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这伤痕也未免太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡多少佐，来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.20,0:06:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是飞马级
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.65,0:06:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很准时啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.45,0:06:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对联邦而言似乎是少有的正经舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.70,0:06:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:06:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼叫U-COM
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:06:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs34\3c&H00ef877e}U-COM：以联邦军Ⅷ级潜艇为舰身设计的潜艇\N可装载MS及拥有良好的秘密作战能力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.15,0:06:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.95,0:06:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是Walfisch
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:06:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦军的飞马级确认
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.80,0:07:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星尘作战开始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.70,0:07:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,92
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.10,0:07:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,93
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,94
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.55,0:07:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,95
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.85,0:07:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,96
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.45,0:07:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贾布罗花了不少钱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能拨少许来这里就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.65,0:07:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.81,0:07:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞马级的吗？大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.35,0:07:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是白色基地的改良型的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非…搭载机是GUNDAM类型？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.95,0:07:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几时能去看看？大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.05,0:07:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下，让我去調查清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待明早的作战简报吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.85,0:07:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天辛苦了，解散
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.00,0:07:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉斯，你想一直趴下去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.13,0:07:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.65,0:08:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉斯，它着陆了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.90,0:08:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.65,0:08:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏！开慢点！宏！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.05,0:08:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你一起总能遇上一些有趣的意外，真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.56,0:08:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.80,0:08:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…去哪里？宏兄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.93,0:08:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.40,0:08:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.74,0:08:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.75,0:08:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的，和你一起不会觉得闷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.60,0:09:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,申报
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.80,0:09:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席那普斯大佐以下乘员211名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.35,0:09:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭载强袭登陆舰阿尔比昂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.40,0:09:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运载二架新型MS按时到达
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.46,0:09:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了，大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.40,0:09:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曼涅里准将
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我申请立即签发核储备库的开封许可
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是由贾布罗带来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许可书及由明天起测试项目的一览表
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,测试机师由你来挑选
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,档案已准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你酌情安排吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以期万全
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是GUNDAM
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.21,0:10:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.99,0:10:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM有两架！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.80,0:10:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧啊，吉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.75,0:10:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs34\3c&H00ef877e}Core Fighter：核心战斗机\N确保驾驶员的安全和回收战斗数据所用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这架装了Core Fighter！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.08,0:10:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架也很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.75,0:10:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个重装甲…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.00,0:10:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不寻常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.30,0:10:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实不寻常啊，那位小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.80,0:10:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是基地的人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.60,0:10:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.22,0:10:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿纳海姆的人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.55,0:10:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不、敝人是测试机师恰克·吉斯少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:10:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，原来是担任测试机师的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.60,0:11:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是系统工程师 妮娜·巴普尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.50,0:11:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才要请你多指教呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.96,0:11:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是同期的宏·浦木少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏！是妮娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.25,0:11:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妮娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿纳海姆的系统工程师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.60,0:11:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请、请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很怕羞，对美人没有抵抗力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.17,0:11:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅对美人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.60,0:11:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GUNDAM正在维护中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.56,0:11:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要参观的话日后再联络你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.80,0:11:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就和我联络吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天几点结束工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.40,0:11:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须定好约会的时间才行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.06,0:11:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去喝啤酒如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.60,0:11:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.70,0:11:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？欧比尔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.35,0:11:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边检查OK了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没其他事的话，我想去散散步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.50,0:11:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊！辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.65,0:11:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散步…这里什么都没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.85,0:11:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.05,0:11:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们这些生活在宇宙的人而言
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.85,0:11:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球上的一切都很新奇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.67,0:12:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了，晚霞！一定是去看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.50,0:12:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多是时候了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.40,0:12:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带你去个看晚霞的最佳场所吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.93,0:12:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，我看不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下嘛，宏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.75,0:12:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说等一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏！你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太缠人是很讨人嫌的，小子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.30,0:12:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟，哟…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.95,0:12:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约会？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.25,0:12:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.50,0:12:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢到抓着我手不放的话就陪你一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.70,0:12:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚霞或是啤酒都行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离这还有一小时行程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.41,0:12:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blau Engel呼叫Walfisch
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.30,0:12:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是Walfisch
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.10,0:13:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blau Engel很顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切照预定行事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.50,0:13:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Walfisch了解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南极条约签署以来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:13:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里还是第一次开启
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.45,0:14:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.50,0:14:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真希望眼前这扇门继续紧闭着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.26,0:14:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧姆中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切记不要大意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只是个边境基地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.30,0:14:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,测试机师的话个个都有一流的技术
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.15,0:14:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您放心！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.80,0:14:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐身负重任
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.90,0:14:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请一定小心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.00,0:14:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫欧比尔吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有大尉的制服了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.65,0:14:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.20,0:14:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了，我也不会因此而改变什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.90,0:14:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待各位的活跃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.60,0:14:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GM换装的背包
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.40,0:14:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推力好强
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.00,0:14:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腿部的震动吸收装置
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.50,0:14:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超高度落下也有充分耐力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:15:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GM已经如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.10,0:15:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型机就更令人期待了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.55,0:15:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型机令人期待是什么意思？中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.20,0:15:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿连中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说过新型机的机师还未定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.50,0:15:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的机师称得上王牌的是大尉您
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.00,0:15:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想这已是定局了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.80,0:15:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想驾驶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.65,0:15:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成天对着讨厌的ZAKU…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.80,0:15:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎哟，ZAKU也是好机体哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.30,0:15:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.76,0:15:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.28,0:15:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是阿纳海姆的系统工程师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.18,0:15:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜·巴普尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.10,0:15:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿纳海姆的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.10,0:15:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为部下的无礼向你致歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.15,0:15:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是指挥测试机师的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴宁格大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.80,0:15:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡克斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.95,0:15:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是失礼了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是摩拉·巴席特中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是由贾布罗来此负责机械整备的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.93,0:15:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后请多多指教，大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.75,0:15:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，可以与您同席吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.06,0:15:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请坐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.80,0:16:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型机的动力似乎提升相当多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背包的测试已经完成了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.10,0:16:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天把它试装在改良型GM上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.01,0:16:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动力提升了好几级
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.12,0:16:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.85,0:16:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说新型机要从这基地里挑选测试机师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想找什么样的机师呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.60,0:16:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能透露一下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.10,0:16:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对本公司来说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是能发挥出新型机最高性能的机师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便是最受欢迎的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.45,0:16:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩拉，该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.65,0:16:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.45,0:16:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.95,0:16:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才想说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.30,0:16:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于用旧型机训练的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.15,0:16:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能将新型机的性能发挥到什么程度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.55,0:16:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点担心而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.05,0:16:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要胡萝卜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.75,0:16:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，打搅一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.40,0:16:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参观的话明天以后再说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.59,0:17:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从GUNDAM的反应速度快了0.5秒左右来看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.86,0:17:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出力提高了三成吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.15,0:17:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GM连三分之二也发挥不出
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.25,0:17:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那重装甲的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用的是对核兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.95,0:17:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肩上的火箭炮是战术核装备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.16,0:17:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是想证实这点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.98,0:17:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是机师吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.89,0:17:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好敏锐的观察力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但谁知道技术方面又如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.50,0:17:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来晚了，抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是阿纳海姆公司的欧比尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.69,0:17:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？晚霞美不美？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.99,0:17:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.40,0:17:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日出也很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那今晚得早点睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.24,0:17:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.25,0:17:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.46,0:18:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟如此松懈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.73,0:18:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦到哪里都是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟和这样的家伙们打到现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.05,0:18:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安装完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.05,0:18:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样算是告一段落了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴普尔顿小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.45,0:18:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天仍有很多事要麻烦你，拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.60,0:18:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.90,0:19:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？在做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的两位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里应该禁止进入的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.85,0:19:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.90,0:19:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1号机这边只装备机枪弹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.10,0:19:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道现正在装备弹头？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.50,0:19:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以别来碍事，快点给我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.20,0:19:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她如果不那么带刺就完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是死心吧，吉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.10,0:19:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说，她讨厌你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.10,0:19:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点我也知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.61,0:19:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去陪我喝闷酒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.50,0:19:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下，再看一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.96,0:19:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好伤心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.10,0:19:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起的MS
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.86,0:20:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也这样认为
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.45,0:20:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火箭炮已装备好弹头了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.90,0:20:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.25,0:20:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么，我就来试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.57,0:20:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个人真是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次又想搞什么新花样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.60,0:20:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.75,0:20:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.90,0:20:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请关掉舱门下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.50,0:20:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.65,0:20:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能听到吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.75,0:20:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我下去！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.65,0:21:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来人啊，谁来阻止2号机！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.60,0:21:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.50,0:21:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.30,0:21:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木少尉？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.25,0:21:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦木少尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.40,0:21:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去叫别人来，以你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.62,0:21:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是机师！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.35,0:21:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正在装弹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.75,0:21:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法立即出动的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请快点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.25,0:21:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2号机的机师，你能听到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.95,0:21:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上下来的话罪责尚轻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在马上从2号机上下来！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.80,0:21:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这架机体和核弹头我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.90,0:21:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了ZION的复兴！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.85,0:21:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZION？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.90,0:21:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左舷格纳库内壁破损
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.90,0:22:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,损伤状况确认中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.90,0:22:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长，格纳库有联络
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.40,0:22:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2号机被自称是ZION的人夺走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.00,0:22:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2号机被夺走了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.25,0:22:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导弹群接近
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.73,0:22:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离一万二千！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.95,0:22:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.80,0:22:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左舷引擎中弹！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.25,0:22:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出力下降
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.45,0:22:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各部报告破损部位
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.35,0:22:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查出导弹发射位置
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.02,0:22:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.01,0:22:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米诺夫斯基粒子散布
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.76,0:22:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.10,0:22:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.00,0:22:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今ZION还想干什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.50,0:22:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席那普斯舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.70,0:22:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请阻止1号机
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.30,0:22:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1号机怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.15,0:22:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,测试机师浦木少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.94,0:22:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算乘坐着去制止2号机
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.15,0:22:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快装备好实弹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.84,0:22:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡克斯，吉斯，快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.36,0:23:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是模拟战！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.50,0:23:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心应付！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.66,0:23:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.20,0:23:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.25,0:23:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大尉，是ZION
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.80,0:23:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZION把装备核弹头的2号机夺走了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.30,0:23:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.22,0:23:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZION？！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.70,0:23:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙又想发动战争吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.00,0:23:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要杀死多少人才罢手！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.80,0:23:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.60,0:23:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.80,0:23:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.50,0:23:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZAKU…吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.10,0:23:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为联邦所用了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.00,0:23:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样子实在不忍目睹
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.70,0:24:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡多少佐！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.10,0:24:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盖利吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.00,0:24:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战成功
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.30,0:24:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.15,0:24:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想从这离开！

